p.em: pool may open new conns up to Max

div.p: Retry Schedule (ConnectDB backoff): attempt 1 immediate 2 500ms 3 1s 4 2s 5 4s FATAL
pgxpool.New(ctx, dsn) config.MaxConns=10 config.MinConns=2 config.MaxConnLifetime=30m config.MaxConnIdleTime=5m config.HealthCheckPeriod=1m
pool.Ping(ctx) succeeds [within 5 attempts] log: "connected to DB" ConnectDB() returns pool
conn.Release() [in-flight drops to 0] conn returned to pool
pool.Acquire(ctx) [in-flight reaches MaxConns=10] next caller blocks
conn.Release() [one slot freed] blocked Acquire() unblocks
pool.Close() [on SIGTERM shutdown] drains in-flight conns
pool.Close() [on SIGTERM shutdown] closes MinConns idle conns
pool.Ping() fails [5 attempts exhausted] fmt.Errorf("connectDB: failed after 5 attempts: %w") log.Fatal os.Exit(1)
